snippet.title: Calmed by the Dark Complete Edition - Trailer
snippet.description:
Calmed by the Dark Complete Edition features a entire new campaign with a new main character.
The main campaing also got additional content as improved social events.
Calmed by the Dark Complete Edition will be released on October 9 2019.

You can download the game here: https://punishedmike.itch.io/calmed-by-the-dark
